{"tid":695600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇習近平整大陸娛樂圈，睇到人心都涼埋","createTime":"2018-06-09T10:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T14:19:37.000Z","uid":73972,"like":179,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0b65dd14ce21f216f6b768c07653c7ea7fce4c","tid":695600,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有d 娛樂圈勢力人士本身仲話要隊冧爆料個人，但見風向唔對，中共有心整頓，嚇到跪哂地同人道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n崔永元前天接受《蘋果》專訪大爆，李晨的軍事電影《獵空天》前顧問、空軍前試飛員徐勇凌下「死亡追殺令」。徐在報道見報後約6小時，分別在昨凌晨5時31分、5時44分、6時26分及7時55分四度在微博發文，第一篇便首度向崔永元道歉，他說：「對於網絡熱點事件，過激地表達憤怒情緒，語言表達並非我本意，對由此引發的負面影響表示愧疚，對當事人所造成的傷害表示歉意，對不起，崔永元！」"},{"pid":"8ed0e835db1e053643359213302a758a8975279e","tid":695600,"uid":8410,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗"},{"pid":"959c3b67527bab7681eb1c91313d90b5f4abec38","tid":695600,"uid":73972,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180609&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20415520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180609%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20415520&d=pmnSWfWqNx0i5qNhJfQyaEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3938989a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180609%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20415520&h=6a9a7751\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180609&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20415520</a><br />\n<br />\n好正<img